data.description: Welcome home to this well maintained Tudor in Richmond Hts.  Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac this 4 bedroom home features 2570 sq. ft of living space and an inground pool!  Convenient access to I-271, Beachwood Place and Legacy Village.  The eat-in kitchen opens to the family room featuring a wood burning fireplace. New furnace and A/C in 2023.
